title: Bruce Lee's audio launch postponed
text: Until yesterday, the audio launch of Ram Charan's most eagerly awaited film, Bruce Lee, was rumored to be taking place either on September 26 or September 27, however, the latest update suggests a slight delay in the film's audio launch, and the fresh date is being discussed by film circles is October 2. The audio launch event is expected to take place at Shilpa Kala Vedika in Hyderabad. Composed by SS Thaman, Bruce Lee's audio will be releasing amidst heavy expectations from fans.
